lih.kg/1639585\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1639585</a><br />\n<br />\n星期二（10月8日）早上，港鐵就宣布提前在晚上八點停駛，點解政府未卜先知出現動亂？其實政府有心製造一個長期嘅亂局，然後用緊急法立更多惡法，其中最近葉國謙就話要準備封網，呢樣嘢可以對香港抗爭造成極嚴重打擊。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><ins>斷網可毒啞香港人，新疆前車可鑑</ins></span></strong><br />\n斷網真係落實嘅話，<span style=\"color: red;\">最惡劣係好似新疆咁徹底斷網</span>，只有政府部門先可以上網，<span style=\"color: red;\">徹底封網的話，大家不但難以互通抗爭消息，而且香港訊息難以傳到海外，香港人也難以接收海外消息。西方人對香港嘅了解，只能經過政府嘅官方說法，或極少數流出嘅真相。</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">新疆早在2009年封網，同時限制境外人士到新疆旅遊，斷絕新疆對外聯繫，結果近年就出現新疆集中營。呢方面大家一定要警惕！</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>大家不能掉以輕心</strong><br />\n或者有人認為政府會顧及香港嘅國際環境唔會輕易斷網，但現在中共已經失去理性，當中央黔驢技窮，損害香港利益而徹底封網並非不可。就好似半年前大家都唸唔到香港已經失去遊行以及戴口罩嘅自由。<br />\n<br />\n本文為節錄，全文請到此瀏覽：<br />\n<br />\n（分析+行動）政府有意部署封網，封網後香港變新疆！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1639585\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1639585</a>"},{"pid":"54be055d497e80622169f537c9abcff6a7c6f2f6","tid":1640911,"uid":205826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:31:55.000Z","msg":"佢認左都冇後果架啦<br />\n傻啦, 快啲將個波扔返俾個垃圾政權啊!!!<br />\n我講你知點解宜家應該打文宣戰<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ekkhBS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ekkhBS</a>"},{"pid":"8ff7725559c9e8cf99053dfc51971431e263258e","tid":1640911,"uid":33868,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:33:41.000Z","msg":"編劇組諗緊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a75ee52c2d47114ac1f0b80ec218b09f6fea3cfa","tid":1640911,"uid":259813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ff7725559c9e8cf99053dfc51971431e263258e","tid":1640911,"uid":33868,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:33:41.000Z","msg":"編劇組諗緊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:35:34.000Z","msg":"謝振中唔響度係差啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da80d670442172a67db47dd73a8841bdaab84830","tid":1640911,"uid":79562,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:42:40.000Z","msg":"一燈即回應<br />\n蓋清<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"316cb77b3260cb216f800e64fbc5b1808b97c49b","tid":1640911,"uid":70988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da80d670442172a67db47dd73a8841bdaab84830","tid":1640911,"uid":79562,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:42:40.000Z","msg":"一燈即回應<br />\n蓋清<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:10:15.000Z","msg":"佢條　team有差佬"}]}